l than the exiting results that are derived specifically for the\ncase of $m=3$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2016 03:34:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2016 05:26:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-15"}
