ar mass at\nthe same epoch. This suggests that the processes which differentiate BCGs from\nnormal massive elliptical galaxies must occur at $z \\lesssim 2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2016 09:36:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2016 12:59:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-27"}
